PLAY;Start a new game or load an existing one
OPTIONS;Set game options, including key bindings
EXTRAS;If you just don't have enough
QUIT;Exit the game
NEW;Start a new campaign
LOAD;Continue an existing save
COLOUR;Save the current ship colour for your campaign
MAIN;Return to main menu
GAME;Play
SAVED;Current ship colour saved
WHEEL;Use the mouse wheel to change
